(17, 'Taylor Made Golf M2 Iron Set Full Review', 'The most popular-priced irons on the market', 'Best Golf Clubs. Golf Clubs', 'taylor-made-golf-m2-iron-set-full-review', 1, 22, 'productCoverImage/XwnJDIMvpTp6QOc5CA1Sf9cyoKcz91kSAE6foTP9.jpeg', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">The <a href=\"https://amzn.to/3cMXsi5\">Taylor Made M2</a> iron sets&nbsp;are possibly one of the most popular-priced irons on the market, and these items are flying off the counters.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Probably the reason is that these&nbsp;irons&nbsp;are the best cavity backs available.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">The TaylorMade M2 Iron Set&nbsp;intends to launch the&nbsp;golf ball&nbsp;as high and as fast as possible for the best distance and steep landing angle.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">These&nbsp;golf iron sets&nbsp;come out to give&nbsp;golfers&nbsp;the whole performance package with low CG,&nbsp;Speed Pocket&nbsp;technology, and&nbsp;Geocoustic engineering&mdash;it&rsquo;s one of the most technologically advanced ranges&nbsp;golf iron sets.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Technologies used in&nbsp;TaylorMade Golf M2 Iron Set&nbsp;act together to develop golfers game reaching into more&nbsp;distance, peak trajectory, and&nbsp;forgiveness.</p>\r\n<h3><span>Technology</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">There are&nbsp;Face Slots&nbsp;in the&nbsp;TaylorMade Golf M2 Iron Set&nbsp;that low the CG and grow&nbsp;consistency&nbsp;forming a thinner overall, topline, and using a more intense&nbsp;speed pocket&nbsp;with a 33% slimmer front wall for even more&nbsp;extensibility.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">The&nbsp;clubhead&nbsp;is lighter, thinner, and wider with a six-sided fluted hosel that saves the extra weight in the iron. There is a 30% correction in bending on the new&nbsp;hosel.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">The M2 Golf iron&nbsp;has Geocoustic engineering techniques that improved through the geometry for a more comforting feeling and sound via 3-D damping and an optimized rib structure to provide astonishing&nbsp;frequencies.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">As a result, these advanced&nbsp;iron set, technology-wise, has the uniqueness of TaylorMade characteristics. The remarkable development in the technology is the less&nbsp;center of gravity&nbsp;placement, 33% lower than the 2016 M2 Irons.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">This lower center of gravity placement enables&nbsp;higher flight. It also has the&nbsp;Face Slot&nbsp;technology, missing from the previous&nbsp;M2 Irons.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">We will describe later on the key features of the&nbsp;TaylorMade M2 Irons, which will mostly be incorporated into the latest technologies applied.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Key Features</h3>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0in;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #0e101a; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">TaylorMade Golf M2 Iron Set&nbsp;is one of the highest iron sets on the track, even among&nbsp;distance focused&nbsp;iron sets.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #0e101a; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Light-weighted&nbsp;irons give&nbsp;golfers&nbsp;better&nbsp;forgiveness&nbsp;with consistent ball speeds and heights even throughout mishits&nbsp;golfers&nbsp;can perform&nbsp;great distance.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #0e101a; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">The TaylorMade Golf M2 Iron Set&nbsp;is good looking with amazing high-tech qualifications.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #0e101a; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">M2 TaylorMade irons&nbsp;are smooth the body, and it is barely noticeable transition from the non-slotted to the&nbsp;slotted irons.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/TaylorMade-M2-Right-Steel-Regular/dp/B07WJJJSH4/ref=as_li_ss_il?dchild=1&amp;keywords=taylormade+golf+m2&amp;qid=1591803565&amp;sr=8-5&amp;th=1&amp;linkCode=li2&amp;tag=bhugolf-20&amp;linkId=88f122d108d727f70bc0fdc184831e05&amp;language=en_US\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"//ws-na.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B07WJJJSH4&amp;Format=_SL160_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=US&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=bhugolf-20&amp;language=en_US\" border=\"0\" /></a><img style=\"border: none !important; margin: 0px !important;\" src=\"https://ir-na.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=bhugolf-20&amp;language=en_US&amp;l=li2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B07WJJJSH4\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Available Shafts</h4>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Golfers&nbsp;can pick between iron or&nbsp;graphite shafts&nbsp;while buying the iron set. Here are your choices with the&nbsp;TaylorMade M2 Irons:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0in;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #0e101a; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><a href=\"https://amzn.to/2XNfdtw\">REAX HL 88 by FST&nbsp;steel shaft</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #0e101a; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><a href=\"https://amzn.to/2AfMncm\">M2 REAX graphite shafts</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Both options intended for&nbsp;high-launch&nbsp;ball aviation, so they are relatively lighter than your typical&nbsp;iron shafts. The graphite alternative is reasonably more costly and significantly&nbsp;light-weighted.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong>The uniqueness of Taylormade M2 Irons&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Various things set the&nbsp;Taylormade M2 Irons&nbsp;aloof from other&nbsp;game improvement&nbsp;irons available.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">The M2 Irons&nbsp;sold as a distance oriented&nbsp;game improvement&nbsp;kit. Generally, distance oriented irons have some fundamental issues, as the heads are most of the adjust more massive MOI and thus making it very troublesome to handle.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">These issues luckily undertaken by the&nbsp;TaylorMade 2018 M2 Irons&nbsp;as the heads are mid-large sized rather than being heavy. Thus they are quite easy to handle. Performance in the&nbsp;distance&nbsp;with forgiveness also managed entirely. They are singularly the&nbsp;longest irons&nbsp;in the market, and the most forgiving.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">The&nbsp;TaylorMade M2 Irons&nbsp;still gives a generous amount of&nbsp;balance&nbsp;to players although, they are not as playable as performance. Particularly concerning control, it is simple to halt the ball anywhere you notice fit, even with the higher than general&nbsp;flight trajectory.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong>Features and Benefits</strong></h3>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">01. Updated Face Slot</h4>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">The face slot&nbsp;is not a new technology for&nbsp;TaylorMade clubs, first launched on the&nbsp;TaylorMade RSi&nbsp;a few years back.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">The 2016 version of the&nbsp;M2 irons&nbsp;didn&rsquo;t highlight the&nbsp;face slot, because the bigger head in joining with the&nbsp;face slot&nbsp;will develop the&nbsp;center of gravity, thus reducing the higher&nbsp;flight trajectory.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">With the new&nbsp;Taylormade M2 irons, this issue has been undertaken with modern developments in the design to&nbsp;lessen the CG.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">The accomplishment is possible by providing the top line of the head and the&nbsp;front edge, 33% slimmer, and the face profile also made with a more&nbsp;simplistic design.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">The&nbsp;hosel&nbsp;is also&nbsp;thinner, and as a result, the CG was reduced by about 7%, letting the face slot to fit in without losing&nbsp;ball height. These designs advancements allow the&nbsp;face slot&nbsp;to feature on the 4 to 8 irons.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">02. Ultra-Thin Speed Pocket</h4>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">There is an&nbsp;ultra-thin&nbsp;Speed Pocket&nbsp;in the 4 to 7 irons.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">The&nbsp;speed pocket, placed in the&nbsp;sole, provides the face to be big, and unsupported and as a result, it is more flexible during the impact.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Because of that, the&nbsp;speed pocket&nbsp;can increase the&nbsp;golf ball&nbsp;speeds all over the face, giving players remarkable speed still on&nbsp;off-center&nbsp;hits.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Thus, the&nbsp;speed pocket&nbsp;is so much necessary for both&nbsp;forgiveness&nbsp;and&nbsp;distance.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">03. New Fluted Hosel</h4>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">The&nbsp;hosel&nbsp;has a&nbsp;fluted&nbsp;design in the&nbsp;Taylormade M2 irons. The thick-thin&nbsp;fluted design&nbsp;made the&nbsp;hosel&nbsp;to achieve&nbsp;less weight&nbsp;and making the offset bigger while still providing a thick top line.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">In the new&nbsp;TaylorMade Golf M2 iron set, the&nbsp;fluted hosel&nbsp;is slimmer, having six more extended parts on comparing with the previous one. Thus, it is more&nbsp;light-weighted&nbsp;and gives the players more easy&nbsp;control&nbsp;over the game.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">So, the&nbsp;lighter hosel&nbsp;gives two things. One is enabling the players to have&nbsp;faster swings&nbsp;and transferring the&nbsp;center of gravity&nbsp;of the&nbsp;club&nbsp;lower.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Pros and Cons of The TaylorMade Golf M2 Iron Set</h4>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Pros</h4>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0in;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #0e101a; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">TaylorMade Golf M2 Iron Set&nbsp;supplies golf players a great, dynamic feel and&nbsp;distance&nbsp;combined with high levels of&nbsp;forgiveness.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #0e101a; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">The TaylorMade M2 iron sets are so much confidence-inspiring behind the ball and confirmed to be easy to hit in the ground. The above-average&nbsp;distance&nbsp;on well-struck shots and slight mishits with a nice feel.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Cons</h4>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0in;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #0e101a; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">It is hard to determine how much of the&nbsp;distance&nbsp;comes from the technology or the stronger lofts from the&nbsp;TaylorMade Golf M2 Iron Set.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">The mid-to-low spin on the clubs decreases the stopping power while hitting the mid and&nbsp;long irons&nbsp;into greens.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0in;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: #953734; background-color: #76923c;\"><strong>&nbsp;Buy Now</strong></span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong>Are&nbsp;<a href=\"https://amzn.to/2XNfdtw\">TaylorMade M2irons</a>&nbsp;suitable for&nbsp;beginners?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">With all the qualities of&nbsp;TaylorMade M2 Iron&nbsp;discussed above, it is very beneficial for&nbsp;beginners. We can say that the&nbsp;design&nbsp;is mostly for newbies.&nbsp;Forgiveness&nbsp;is the most necessary characteristics for&nbsp;beginners, and&nbsp;M2 golf iron sets&nbsp;have this feature. The&nbsp;forgiveness&nbsp;process is simple.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">It produces exceptional ball&nbsp;flight, and speeds even on mishits. It is possible because of the&nbsp;face slot&nbsp;and&nbsp;speed pocket, allowing the&nbsp;face slot&nbsp;to be more&nbsp;flexible&nbsp;more than usual.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Another major feature for&nbsp;newcomers, particularly in this modern age of golf, is&nbsp;distance. By creating enough distance,&nbsp;beginners&nbsp;can get satisfied enough by their performance, maintaining the concern to develop more.&nbsp;The M2 iron sets&nbsp;are some of the&nbsp;longest irons&nbsp;in the market, so performance in the&nbsp;distance&nbsp;is not a problem.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong>Are TaylorMade M2 irons \"game improvement\"?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Yes, the&nbsp;TaylorMade Golf M2 Iron Set&nbsp;is a&nbsp;game improvement, mainly defined by the cavity-back design.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">The shorter irons&nbsp;in&nbsp;the best golf irons&nbsp;set surely use a cavity back design with a hole that closes in. The&nbsp;longer irons&nbsp;used a cavity-back/blade hybrid design, to enable a more reliable transition throughout the set.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong>Are&nbsp;TaylorMade M2 Iron Sets&nbsp;forged?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">No,&nbsp;TaylorMade M2 Irons&nbsp;not forged. The iron used there is&nbsp;cast iron. Some will fancy&nbsp;forged irons&nbsp;for their active feel. But, cast irons are becoming more popular these days because of their durability. The newer technologies to make&nbsp;cast irons&nbsp;also provide less compromise on feel and sound.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong>Is there any graphite shaft in the&nbsp;TaylorMade M2 Iron Set?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Yes,&nbsp;TaylorMade Golf M2 Iron Sets&nbsp;come with&nbsp;graphite shafts. They are somewhat more pricey but worth each cent. The default&nbsp;graphite shaft&nbsp;in the&nbsp;TaylorMade Golf M2 Iron Sets&nbsp;is M2 REAX (74-45 G). The shaft is available in S, R, A, and L flex.</p>', 'Are you looking for best suggestion on selecting the  best golf clubs for beginners. We write review the 5 top rated sets of beginner\'s clubs for 2020', 'https://amzn.to/3cMXsi5', 2, 1, '2020-06-10 09:49:34', '2020-07-07 08:16:19', NULL),
