ble to hit.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Golf players&nbsp;will find super game improvement irons that have a cavity backing with wide soles, and perimeter weighting that gives forgiveness and off-center hits. Not only the quantity of iron in the set is notable, but also the styling of the irons is essential to know as it gives&nbsp;super support&nbsp;to improve the game for the&nbsp;freshman golfers&nbsp;to start their golfing adventure.</span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Putter</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">There is a mallet putter in the&nbsp;Callaway Men\'s Strata 12-Piece Complete Golf&nbsp;Set. The&nbsp;putter&nbsp;does not seem to have much press, but finally, it is an excellent tool for&nbsp;new golfers. The face of the&nbsp;putter&nbsp;is a little bit bouncy, but golf players get used to it in no time. In short, it is precisely what any&nbsp;golf player&nbsp;looks for in a&nbsp;putter: perfect&nbsp;accuracy&nbsp;and distance.</span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bag</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The&nbsp;backpack strap&nbsp;makes the&nbsp;stand bag&nbsp;very easy to carry, and it is very comfortable on the shoulders for the carrier. The stand on the bag works like magic which, makes it very easy to carry on the&nbsp;golf field&nbsp;without touching the ground.</span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Accessories</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The best feature of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://amzn.to/3hjqnxA\">Callaway Men\'s Strata Complete Golf Set</a>&nbsp;includes some astounding accessories like a rain hood and a cooler pocket. The multi-pocketed bag helps newcomers to take all they need at a time to the course like extra golf balls and other valuables.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">For the&nbsp;newcomer golfers, an astonishing&nbsp;quality&nbsp;stand bag&nbsp;is great for the range and helps keeps&nbsp;golf&nbsp;players&nbsp;clubs dry without damaging the&nbsp;club set. The&nbsp;club head&nbsp;covers are also very convenient to golfers because it keeps the woods clean. It also keeps the Woods without dings that affect the appearance and performance of the&nbsp;club.</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Features and Benefits</h3>\r\n<p><strong style=\"color: #1d2228;\"> </strong></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">01. 460cc Titanium Driver</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Beginner golfers need to have a driver in a&nbsp;complete golf club set&nbsp;though it comes with a slight warning. Most&nbsp;novice players&nbsp;are not going to able to hit with the driver with any consistency, and thought of immediately opening the&nbsp;Callaway Men\'s Strata Complete Golf Set&nbsp;and heading to the actual range with the intent of using the driver is slightly insane.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The driver in&nbsp;Callaway Men\'s Strata Complete Golf Set&nbsp;is 10.5 degrees. And it is made from&nbsp;titanium, which measures 460cc in volume. It also has a large clubhead, and it gives a&nbsp;sweet spot&nbsp;with the best forgiveness off the&nbsp;tee box. To master the drive, it certainly takes some time for the&nbsp;golfers, and over time the drive works admirably for its player.</span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">02. Low profile 3-wood</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The 3-wood in the&nbsp;Callaway Men\'s Strata Complete Golf Set&nbsp;lofts at 15.5 degrees, making it a more trustworthy club for&nbsp;high&nbsp;handicappers&nbsp;and provide length to the golfers to take the next step in their craft level.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">With that much low profile that keeps the&nbsp;center of gravity&nbsp;toward the back of the club, the 3-wood from&nbsp;Callaway Men\'s Strata Complete Golf Set&nbsp;helps novice players to get the ball into the air for&nbsp;maximum distance&nbsp;and carry on drives flawlessly.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The 3-wood gives great comfortable feeling on the&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">tee box</strong><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;and certainly provide useful service from the fairway as a&nbsp;golf player\'s&nbsp;game grows.</span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">03. Wide Soled 5-hybrid</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The 5-hybrid of the&nbsp;Callaway Men\'s Strata Complete Golf Set&nbsp;takes the position of a 5-iron that is harder to hit for&nbsp;beginner golfers. Though the 5-hybrid provides reliable connection at impact and the construction of the club enables the wide sole of the&nbsp;clubhead&nbsp;to slide beneath the&nbsp;golf ball&nbsp;for a more dependable launch angle and more ball climax.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">As players getting more experienced in the&nbsp;golf games, the 5-hybrid gradually becomes incredibly essential allowing players a trustworthy club to use it on the&nbsp;tee box&nbsp;and from the fairway on longer par-4s and par-5s.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">There is not much difference between the hybrid and the set&rsquo;s 6-iron with lofted at 26 degrees, but the way of the&nbsp;clubhead&nbsp;unquestionably gives an improvement for the&nbsp;amateur golfers&nbsp;that iron cannot provide.</span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">04. Cavity-Backed Irons</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">In the&nbsp;Callaway Men\'s Strata Complete 12-piece Golf Set, the four irons have a 6-iron and a 9-iron.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">All of them are cavity-backed, forcing extra steel to the outer end of the&nbsp;clubhead&nbsp;for a better experience and most forgiveness.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #1d2228; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">These four irons build to help the high handicapper as a game improver to get the ball into the air smoothly and help have it upright with a target that goes where&nbsp;golf players&nbsp;aim.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #1d2228;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B07H29Z4Y2/ref=as_li_ss_il?ie=UTF8&amp;th=1&amp;linkCode=li2&amp;tag=bhugolf-20&amp;linkId=ecba32236d5d27875490586865bc87f4&amp;language=en_US\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"//ws-na.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B07H29Z4Y2&amp;Format=_SL160_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=US&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=bhugolf-20&amp;language=en_US\" border=\"0\" /></a><img style=\"border: none !important; margin: 0px !important;\" src=\"https://ir-na.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=bhugolf-20&amp;language=en_US&amp;l=li2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B07H29Z4Y2\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /></span><br /><br /></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">05. Perimeter-weighted Pitching Wedge</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The Strata Set&rsquo;s pitching wedge has a loft of 44 degrees that performs fine anywhere on the field. The&nbsp;pitching wedge&nbsp;is also the most massive iron in the&nbsp;complete golf club set, and it supports the novice players find some precision while adding a little distance to the amateur players a&nbsp;short game. The pitching wedge in the&nbsp;Callaway Men\'s Strata Complete Golf Set&nbsp;can give a&nbsp;novice golfer&nbsp;100 yards to the green.</span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">06. Blade-Style Putter</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The blade-style&nbsp;putter&nbsp;in the&nbsp;complete golf club set&nbsp;has some extension steel behind its face that provides balance to help to level the flat stick on the field. The shaft of the&nbsp;putter&nbsp;is 35 inches. This measure is standard for an off-the-shelf putter.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Usually, most putters are a whole set struggle to give quality work throughout the field. But, the Strata Set&rsquo;s putter does a great job to roll and getting the&nbsp;golf ball&nbsp;to the cup flawlessly.</span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">07. Lightweight Multi-Pocketed Stand Bag</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The bag in the&nbsp;complete golf set&nbsp;has a lightweight and has several pockets of varying lengths that can carry extra&nbsp;equipment&nbsp;like&nbsp;rain gear, towels, balls, and tees. The bag has a&nbsp;rain hood, five pockets, a cooler pocket, and a backpack strap system.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #1d2228; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The stand bag is great for players as it has two strong legs, which can help with a little exercise on the course.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #1d2228; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The bag will also keep the clubs dry as it does not touch the dewy ground.</span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">08. Two Head Covers</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The two&nbsp;headcovers&nbsp;shield the top two Woods added in the complete golf set. The headcovers are essential to protect the woods as they are the largest clubs in the bag, and the hardness of traveling can damage them.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The headcovers can significantly lower the chances of damaging the&nbsp;Wood&rsquo;s club&nbsp;heads and prolong the life of the&nbsp;clubs&nbsp;by keeping them safe.</span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">09. Complete Starter Set for Beginner and High Handicapper</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Straight from the box, this excellent&nbsp;complete golf club set&nbsp;typically covers every need for a beginner golfer and high handicapper to improve their game.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The Callaway Men\'s Strata Complete Golf Set&nbsp;provides any golfer with one wedge, four irons, three Woods, and a putter, which assures that the&nbsp;golfer&nbsp;has everything they need for their&nbsp;golfing&nbsp;adventure.</span></p>\r\n<h3>Pros and Cons of The Callaway Men\'s Strata Complete Golf Set</h3>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pros</h4>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #1d2228; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The driver will help knock above the player\'s weight in terms of distance and&nbsp;persistence.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #1d2228; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">With the&nbsp;perimeter weighting, the four irons have a precise mixture of forgiveness and&nbsp;balance.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #1d2228; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The hybrid is an excellent&nbsp;small club&nbsp;with user-friendly tricky lies.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #1d2228; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The bag is shoulder-friendly and easy to carry with a range of features and accessories like&nbsp;head covers&nbsp;and&nbsp;rain hood.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #1d2228; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The&nbsp;price&nbsp;is very&nbsp;affordable&nbsp;for an astounding&nbsp;quality&nbsp;product.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cons:</h4>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #1d2228; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The 3-wood is kind of hard to hit, and that does not give&nbsp;golf players&nbsp;enough forgiveness.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #1d2228; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The&nbsp;shaft&nbsp;of the driver is springy, which would not suit the fast swinging of the&nbsp;club.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: #1d2228; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The&nbsp;shaft chip&nbsp;can damage easily and need servicing.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Finally:</h4>\r\n<p style=\"color: #1d2228; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The <a href=\"https://amzn.to/3hjqnxA\">Callaway Men\'s Strata Complete Golf Set</a>&nbsp;is standard and well designed. The tools on the&nbsp;complete golf club set&nbsp;to offer better flight and accuracy. The hybrids and included Woods are light and aerodynamic. The 460cc Driver is a reliable and sturdy golf club. Also, the stand bag is unique and made of heavy material and lightweight for a smooth experience.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The product can support the beginner golfers excellently. Undoubtedly,&nbsp;The Callaway Men\'s Strata Complete Golf Set&nbsp;recommend for novice players for its amazing features.</span></p>', 'Are you looking for best suggestion on selecting the  best golf clubs for beginners. We write review the 5 top rated sets of beginner\'s clubs for 2020', 'https://amzn.to/2AZLFQc', 3, 1, '2020-06-10 21:43:05', '2020-07-07 08:18:01', NULL);
