(38, 'LUCKFY Home Golf Putting Mats Indoor Backyard Golf Practice Training Aid Equipment', 'The Best perfect practice putting mat', 'Perfect practice putting mat, practice putting mat', 'luckfy-home-golf-putting-mats-indoor-backyard-golf-practice-training-aid-equipment', 5, 37, 'productCoverImage/b9AGOUVzueSXRbTmolqyo6q99Uo6stmBWHnGYkRI.jpeg', '<p>Let\'s describe the details review of the&nbsp;<strong>perfect practice putting mat</strong>&nbsp;in today\'s article, here we go!</p>\r\n<h4>Product overview:</h4>\r\n<p>LUCKFY Home Golf Putting Mats is a dual-speed Putting Mat featuring two ball holes effectively on its rubber backed Turf prepared artificial grass surface.</p>\r\n<p>The most durable structure and the sustainability of this product make it is more capable of supporting you at your&nbsp;<strong>Backyard golf practice.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The in-build ball return auto-mechanism included in this&nbsp;<strong>top-rated putting mat&nbsp;</strong>offer each player receive the ball automatically without moving from the starting position.</p>\r\n<p>The inclined plane of this mat makes the speed of each shot difficult to reach the holes. Therefore, the player feels more challenging to reach the hole, increasing their practicing frequency.</p>\r\n<p>Moreover, it can smoothly enhance more fun, more challenging, and more focusing on the Golf practicing. The more fantastic features of this mat are that it can use wherever you wish.</p>\r\n<p>It is applicable for both indoor and outdoor use. Even you don\'t need to take any professional coach, no need to afford a high expanse to practice onto this putting mat.</p>\r\n<p>The package content of this product comes with one Home Golf Putting Mat, 6 golf balls and user guideline, etc.</p>\r\n<h4>Product specification:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Material type: Plastic base + Artificial grass</li>\r\n<li>Product size: 2.5m and 3m</li>\r\n<li>Packing size: 42.5 * 10 * 62cm</li>\r\n<li>Product weight: 4kg</li>\r\n<li>Applic