ee into its package content. Moreover, an easy assembling of this product helps all users to start their playing instantly, de-packing this mat from the manufacturing package. Men, women, or kids everyone can feel lovely using this Golf mat in their Backyard, Lawn or Indoor.</p>\r\n<ol start=\"6\">\r\n<li>\r\n<h4><strong> </strong>Slim Design:</h4>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Slim is beauty; slim is smartness! This proverb is a hundred percent applicable for this putting mat. The slim and compact design of this product makes you capable of rolling this mat easy to store in the carrying bag securely and effortlessly.</p>\r\n<ol start=\"7\">\r\n<li><strong> </strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Affordable:</strong></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>LUCKFY Golf Putting mat can value each penny very effectively. The Long Alignment line, Multi-hole positions moreover the six free training balls makes this product very affordable to meet your requirement.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol start=\"8\">\r\n<li>\r\n<h4><strong> </strong>Easy-to-use:</h4>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>No assistance, you will need to use this practice mat. It\'s a simple and easy mat; anybody can instantly use it simply de-packing from the box. Moreover, the easy-rolling up of this mat helps the user storing this product in the carrying bag for a suitable transporting.</p>\r\n<h4>Pros:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Automatic ball return.</li>\r\n<li>Two ball Holes.</li>\r\n<li>Multi-use.</li>\r\n<li>Two different specifications.</li>\r\n<li>Six free practicing balls.</li>\r\n<li>Applicable for indoor and outdoor use.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Cons:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Maybe two narrows for some users.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'The perfect practice putting mat now very available just around yourself! Follow my article; it will help you to select the preferable mat for your Golf practice.', 'https://amzn.to/2AX3r71', 1, 0, '2020-06-21 10:11:27', '2020-07-04 07:25:40', NULL);
