(39, 'GoSports BattleChip Backyard Golf Cornhole Game', 'GoSports BattleChip Backyard Golf Cornhole Game', 'backyard golf game, yard golf game, backyard golf chipping game, yard game golf balls string, yard golf game rules, aqua golf backyard golf game, backyard mini golf game', 'gosports-battlechip-backyard-golf-cornhole-game', 5, 38, 'productCoverImage/weh3IsZPAkPUDhnpUq8UENaj0tp2dueC9tt4Wqiv.jpeg', '<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/GoSports-BattleChip-Backyard-Cornhole-Abilities/dp/B07WKPKLWJ?th=1\">GoSports BattleChip Backyard</a> Golf Cornhole Game is a new hybrid invention of Golf and Cornhole games giving you the taste of any classic yard gaming with a flavour of the Golf!&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">So, it is saying that Golf meeting Cornhole. How pretty it is! So, you can arrange a BattleChip indoor or outdoor golf games tournament with your 2 or 4 of your friends or family members so make fun to go for the winner.&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">GoSports launched a profound way to enhance the game with some fun and enjoyment. Most people love this chipping game because this game can play around the house even in the backyard as well.&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Both the child and the older person anyone can play this game and can love to feel a competitive gaming time passing.&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">There are several fantastic reviews already are available online. It\'s a good product; all are really happy playing with this.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">This gaming tool has a lightweight and attractive design. Playing this game does not need to go into any complicated process. Moreover, this game can improve the chipping of the player sharpen clearly.</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">In this time of home quarantine, Chippo Golf or Backyard Golf what you say is a perfect way to pass the time joyfully. BattleChip Backyard Golf Cornhole Game is the amazing tools; even your neighbours are not going to pissed-off from your gaming sound or gaming destruction on their boundary wall.&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The balls use in this game, don\'t hit anything. Moreover, the player can drink juice/coffee even can eat fruits or cookies while they are playing a little indoor Cornhole game in their backyard.</span></p>\r\n<h3><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Key features:</span></h3>\r\n<h4><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Hybrid of Golf with Cornhole gaming:</span></h4>\r\n<p><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">GoSports BattleChip Match offers the player to enjoy a hybrid between Golf and Cornhole. A taste of a combination of Golf and Cornhole effectively enhances the gaming taste in your home yard or back yard. It\'s a gaming tool, successfully involved 2 to 4 persons for a successful chipping competition.</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">As GoSports is not included the chipping iron with this game. You can select the chipping iron from any reputed brand. Our suggestion is- Wedge, Sand Wedge, and a Lob Wedge if you want a better result.</span></p>\r\n<h3><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ideal for all age limit:</span></h3>\r\n<p><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Though I have started saying that I have brought this gaming device for my kids, but believe me, my kids are not the only players who play with this tool! My hubby and I also in love with our Chippo Golf now a day. This top-rated combo game is applicable for all ages. Children up to 3 years or an older person, can take an equal opportunity to build up their chipping ability.</span></p>\r\n<h3><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Skill booster:</span></h3>\r\n<p><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Who thought GoSports BattleChip only brought some fun in the game flavour to all players, perhaps they would be shocked to know of this feature!&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">A BattleChip Match offers the user tow target points; it amazingly doubles the game fun and makes a gaming condition so that player can boost up their chipping skills in a comprehensive way. BattleChip Match is featuring multiple scoring pockets along with some numerous ways to play the game.</span></p>\r\n<h3><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Offer Tournament play:</span></h3>\r\n<p><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Enjoy BattleChip Match tournaments with your whole family and closes friends. Count 1 for heati