(49, 'Under Armour UA Rival Polo', 'Under Armour UA Rival Polo', 'best womens golf shirts, best ladies golf shirts, best women\'s golf shirts, Women\'s Golf Polo', 'under-armour-ua-rival-polo', 4, 40, 'productCoverImage/Yz5xINxoMP0ir9s0FCCblYxMUgKFpuFgNXlYlHoR.jpeg', '<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. Under Armour UA Rival Polo</h3>\r\n<p>One of the most famous polo shirts for women and suitable for serious golfers. The manufacturer Under Armour has a reputation in manufacturing quality items for their customer, and this polo shirt is also no exception. Due to its elegant and heavy duty manufacture, you will receive a professional look in the golf course.</p>\r\n<p>The magic is in the fabric of the polo shirt. It will quickly absorb sweat and stop the formation of bacteria. As a result, bad odors can\'t spread, and you will feel fresh for a whole day. Also, you will not feel any disturbance due to the bad odor, and you can entirely focus on your game. The material is robust and wrinkle-resistant.</p>\r\n<p>Taking care of the polo short is too straightforward. Simply give it a machine wash with warm water and detergent, flatten it under the sun, and dry without taking much time. In each sleeve, it consists of mesh that is offering additional breathability. Because of its wrinkle-free feature, you can effortlessly put it into your tote bag, and ironing is not required before wearing it.</p>\r\n<h4>The Pros:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Blocks growth of odor-causing bacteria.</li>\r\n<li>Soft fabric.</li>\r\n<li>Lightweight material.</li>\r\n<li>Dropped scoop hem.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>The Cons:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Inaccurate size chart.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'While playing golf, you need to wearing the right clothes. If you are a woman and fond of playing golf, then you need Best Womens Golf Shirts', 'https://amzn.to/2BErVBW', 34, 0, '2020-07-03 09:35:19', '2020-07-06 07:20:28', NULL),
